  "texts": [
    "Digital protection strategies focus on energy-efficient machine learning models and resilient intrusion detection systems to reduce the environmental impact, addressing SDG 9 and SDG 12.",
    "In the energy and space sectors, cyber-resilience and AI-driven threat detection safeguard critical renewable energy infrastructures, aligning with SDG 7 and SDG 13.",
    "Smart grids benefit from cryptographic chips and dynamic security measures that ensure the resilience and efficiency of decentralized energy networks, contributing to SDG 7 and SDG 9.",
    "Finally, the digital economy's focus on data security and energy-efficient digital systems supports SDG 3 and SDG 12, particularly in areas such as healthcare and resource management.",
    "These themes illustrate how cybersecurity can evolve to meet both technological and environmental goals through innovative, resilient, and sustainable approaches."
